# radroots_net

This is the README for `radroots_net`, which provides network orchestration and
runtime interfaces for the `radroots` core libraries.

## Overview

 * networking configuration and builders;
 * runtime-aware network handle and lifecycle support;
 * optional Nostr client integration and key management helpers;
 * optional logging and runtime-path persistence integration.

